TVB PhTh ChUrBH VShLVH-BH MBYTh ML'a ZBChY-UrYB.
'yBD-MShKYL YMShL BBN MBYSh VBThVK 'aChYM YChLQ NChLH.
MTShUrPh LKSPh VKVUr LZHB VBChN LBVTh YHVH.
MUr'y MQShYB 'yL-ShPhTh-'aVN ShQUr MZYN 'yL-LShVN HVTh.
L'yG LUrSh ChUrPh 'yShHV ShMCh L'aYD L'a YNQH.
'yTUrTh ZQNYM BNY BNYM VThPh'aUrTh BNYM 'aBVThM.
L'a-N'aVH LNBL ShPhTh-YThUr 'aPh KY-LNDYB ShPhTh-ShQUr.
'aBN-ChN HShChD B'yYNY B'yLYV 'aL-KL-'aShUr YPhNH YShKYL.
MKSH-PhSh'y MBQSh 'aHBH VShNH BDBUr MPhUrYD 'aLVPh.
ThChTh G'yUrH BMBYN MHKVTh KSYL M'aH.
'aK-MUrY YBQSh-Ur'y VML'aK 'aKZUrY YShLCh-BV.
PhGVSh DB ShKVL B'aYSh V'aL-KSYL B'aVLThV.
MShYB Ur'yH ThChTh TVBH L'a-ThMYSh Ur'yH MBYThV.
PhVTUr MYM Ur'aShYTh MDVN VLPhNY HThGL'y HUrYB NTVSh.
MTShDYQ UrSh'y VMUrShY'y TShDYQ ThV'yBTh YHVH GM-ShNYHM.
LMH-ZH MChYUr BYD-KSYL LQNVTh ChKMH VLB-'aYN.
BKL-'yTh 'aHB HUr'y V'aCh LTShUrH YVLD.
'aDM ChSUr-LB ThVQ'y KPh 'yUrB 'yUrBH LPhNY Ur'yHV.
'aHB PhSh'y 'aHB MTShH MGBYH PhThChV MBQSh-ShBUr.
'yQSh-LB L'a YMTSh'a-TVB VNHPhK BLShVNV YPhVL BUr'yH.
YLD KSYL LThVGH LV VL'a-YShMCh 'aBY NBL.
LB ShMCh YYTB GHH VUrVCh NK'aH ThYBSh-GUrM.
